----------------------------------------------------------------------
ErdNodeFlips - a simple little Node JS tutorial I'm working on.

This is a simple Node JS tutorial I'm working on which, when complete will allow the user to save a lit of items they need to remember. I.e. Yet another todo list!

The areas tackled in this tutorial are:
 - CouchDB
 - HAML
 - Routing

You can find more info here:
http://www.robsearles.com/2010/05/28/nodejs-tutorial-erdnodeflips/

To install the tutorial, simply clone this repository and then load in the submodules with:
$ git submodule init

